You can set Cubase key commands by going to '''File / Key Commands'''

In the window that appears you can search for key commands and assign them.
You can also set the key commands to reflect other DAW platforms such as Pro Tools,Sonar or Logic by clicking the templates menu and selecting the template you want. (Image below). 


